OL,10,     Gagainst time.
OL,11,G0145FAlexander Armstrong in India
OL,12,     GOn the second leg of his
OL,13,     Gadventure, Alexander visits
OL,14,     GJaipur's Pink City with its
OL,15,     Gdazzling Gem Palace, then heads
OL,16,     Gsouth to explore silk in
OL,17,     GKarnataka and ventures in to
OL,18,     Gtiger country.
